{"tid":1651713,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"將軍澳有懷疑警員被人追打　頭破血流","createTime":"2019-10-13T12:23:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T14:35:48.000Z","uid":184679,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9935f7ec8817ef865eac98ac9259edf25a5f2f0b","tid":1651713,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:23:22.000Z","msg":"示威者晚上繼續在多個地方聚集，在將軍澳，晚上7時許，有一名懷疑是警員的男子，在唐俊街被人追打，該名男子頭破血流，腳部流血。<br />\n<br />\n有人在相信屬該名男子的背包中，找到一枝疑似伸縮警棍，並將它掉在坑渠。警員其後到場圍成防線，嘗試從坑渠檢回伸縮警棍。<br />\n<br />\n在觀塘，警方晚上7時許一度舉長槍，指現場人士涉嫌非法集結，其後跑入內街制服一名男子，並將他帶上警車。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485941-20191013.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485941-20191013.htm&d=uxh%2FksCcDU8UuFRsnlXnuUUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=56eee538\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485941-20191013.htm&h=2fc900bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485941-20191013.htm</a>"},{"pid":"051e69ed6abd0674f10984f4562725a869851033","tid":1651713,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:32:22.000Z","msg":"【以正視聽】已FC！今日割頸嘅係中共特務嫁禍示威者所為，早前連登巴打已預告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1651683\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1651683</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b1578af7996719dbf782b5ea7e69cc5d91e29506","tid":1651713,"uid":27664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:08:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">好多背景聲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n夠啦...  <br />\n夠啦...  夠啦... <br />\n夠啦...  夠啦...  夠啦...  <br />\n夠啦...  夠啦...  <br />\n夠啦...  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係大愛呀</span>"},{"pid":"a851632eccc0b76d856dd956892a8e2956e909